      • setDirectionMarkerSize

        public void setDirectionMarkerSize(double markerSize)
        Parameters:
        markerSize - A double value between 0 and 0.5. When useProportionalDirectionMarkers is true, the size of the marker for a certain edge E will be markerSize * lengthOf(E). Otherwise it's markerSize * lengthOfTheLongestEdge
